name: nre-data-feeds
notes:
National Rail Enquiries (NRE) support the principle of transparency and contribute to the wider industry agenda by making data openly available in the public domain.

NRE have a selection of APIs and XML feeds that are available for use by third party developers to create their own applications.

The data feeds are derived from our three primary engines; Darwin, KB and OJP.
title: NRE Data Feeds
